Package: multiversePlots
Title: Multiverse Density + Heatmap-Strips Plots for Robustness Analyses
Version: 0.1.3
Authors@R: 
    person("Peijia", "Shi", email = "Peijia.Shi@campus.lmu.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Create multiverse analysis plots combining a top density plot 
    (with shaded area for significant results) and stacked heatmap strips 
    for analytical decisions. Includes hurricane and beauty use-cases.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
